Privacy Policy for Font Hunter

Last Updated: [Current Date]

1. Data Collection
Font Hunter does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. The extension only reads font information from the currently active webpage and displays it locally in the popup interface.

2. Information Usage
The only information accessed is the font-related CSS properties of elements on the current webpage. This information is:
- Only used to display font names in the extension popup
- Never stored beyond the current session
- Never transmitted to any external servers

3. Third-Party Services
The extension provides links to Google Search for font information. Users who click these links will be subject to Google's privacy policy.

4. Permissions
The extension requires only the minimum necessary permissions:
- "activeTab": To read font information from the current tab
- "tabs": To display the popup interface

5. Data Storage
No data is stored locally or remotely by this extension.

6. Updates
This privacy policy may be updated to reflect changes in the extension's functionality. Users will be notified of any significant changes.

7. Contact
For questions about this privacy policy, contact: [Your Email]
